I always assumed

89
00:07:00,020 --> 00:07:01,470
Yan Xun was in love

90
00:07:01,790 --> 00:07:03,260
with me.

91
00:07:04,620 --> 00:07:06,480
I didn’t realize until today

92
00:07:08,370 --> 00:07:09,530
that it was only

93
00:07:09,530 --> 00:07:10,690
my wishful thinking.

94
00:07:13,690 --> 00:07:16,920
Look how lucky you are.

95
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,970
I love you so much.

96
00:07:21,090 --> 00:07:22,370
