101
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,690
What should I do,

102
00:07:43,690 --> 00:07:44,600
Huanhuan?

103
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:49,330
Mother.

104
00:07:49,790 --> 00:07:50,840
Why did you call me back

105
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:51,840
in such haste?

106
