110
00:08:02,380 --> 00:08:03,620
Stay close to me.

111
00:08:03,620 --> 00:08:04,870
Don’t run around.

112
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,740
Chun has locked herself

113
00:08:09,740 --> 00:08:10,920
in her room for days.

114
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,190
What happened?

115
00:08:16,290 --> 00:08:18,080
You know girls.

116
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:19,780
They can be sentimental sometimes.

117
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,250
Troubled?

118
00:08:31,980 --> 00:08:33,170
What trouble can it be?

119
00:08:33,830 --> 00:08:35,450
Yan Xun used to

120
00:08:35,450 --> 00:08:36,290
take me to eat

121
00:08:36,290 --> 00:08:38,110
the iced lotus seed soup.

122
00:08:39,350 --> 00:08:41,110
He told me stories

123
00:08:41,110 --> 00:08:42,350
and jokes.

124
00:08:42,690 --> 00:08:44,130
And he gave me

125
00:08:44,130 --> 00:08:45,130
tons of gifts.

126
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,160
But now...

127
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,660
Since that maid Xing’er

128
00:08:50,660 --> 00:08:51,800
showed up,

129
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:54,040
Yan Xun and I

130
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:55,860
have become alienated.

131
00:08:56,660 --> 00:08:58,660
Today, he said

132
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:01,120
he regarded me as his sister.

133
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:05,650
Who’d want to be his sister?

134
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,220
Princess.

135
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,660
Open the door.

136
00:09:13,660 --> 00:09:14,600
Aye.

137
00:09:32,100 --> 00:09:33,760
This year’s Maojian Tea

138
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:35,550
tastes good.

139
00:09:38,020 --> 00:09:40,590
Song, Chun,

140
00:09:41,860 --> 00:09:43,670
do you two

141
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:46,510
take your extravagant lifestyle

142
00:09:46,630 --> 00:09:48,350
for granted?

143
00:09:51,540 --> 00:09:53,330
You can enjoy iced food

144
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:55,670
in the scorching summer

145
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:58,050
that others can’t even imagine.

146
00:09:58,970 --> 00:10:00,440
We are born into the imperial family.

147
00:10:00,580 --> 00:10:02,030
So we’re indeed more blessed

148
00:10:02,030 --> 00:10:03,170
than commoners.

149
00:10:05,300 --> 00:10:06,780
Wait, mother,

150
00:10:06,910 --> 00:10:08,240
don’t you have something important

151
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,780
to tell us?

152
00:10:10,610 --> 00:10:11,680
But

153
00:10:12,130 --> 00:10:13,210
why are you

154
00:10:13,210 --> 00:10:14,410
going off-topic?

155
00:10:14,410 --> 00:10:15,270
Mother,

156
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:17,150
what’s your point?

157
00:10:18,060 --> 00:10:20,130
I just want to remind you two

158
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:22,410
that you are

159
00:10:22,660 --> 00:10:25,440
the Prince and the Princess of Wei.

160
00:10:26,740 --> 00:10:28,370
You own unimaginable

161
00:10:28,370 --> 00:10:30,440
power and wealth.

162
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,240
The world

163
00:10:33,420 --> 00:10:35,120
