164
00:10:36,180 --> 00:10:38,530
That’s not true.

165
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:40,600
There are too many things that I don’t like,

166
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,540
but the one I really want is unavailable.

167
00:10:43,290 --> 00:10:45,410
People always envy the imperial family,

168
00:10:46,970 --> 00:10:49,780
but nobody understands

169
00:10:49,780 --> 00:10:51,120
the suffering

170
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:52,100
we have to endure.

171
00:10:53,500 --> 00:10:55,650
Song, Chun,

172
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:58,100
keep this in mind.

173
00:10:59,590 --> 00:11:01,540
You can get hold of

174
00:11:01,540 --> 00:11:03,150
what commoners can’t

175
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:05,150
except for two things

176
00:11:05,570 --> 00:11:07,600
which are at their fingertips

177
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,320
that you must

178
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:11,910
put behind you.

179
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,700
What are these two things?

180
00:11:19,140 --> 00:11:20,200
Friendship

181
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,530
and love.

182
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:27,100
You must discard love

183
00:11:27,510 --> 00:11:29,160
and never get involved in it.

184
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:32,040
Why?

185
00:11:32,680 --> 00:11:33,820
Love is the most complicated thing

186
00:11:34,610 --> 00:11:36,480
in this world.

187
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,570
You can’t control it

188
00:11:39,570 --> 00:11:40,960
no matter how powerful you are.

189
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,150
Once trapped by it,

190
00:11:43,450 --> 00:11:44,340
you will be caught

191
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:46,540
between love and loyalty,

192
00:11:46,990 --> 00:11:48,690
leading to a disastrous end.

193
00:11:49,300 --> 00:11:51,200
It will not only hurt you,

194
00:11:51,330 --> 00:11:52,860
but also everyone

195
00:11:53,030 --> 00:11:55,470
around you.

196
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:58,740
But it’s human nature to love.

197
00:11:58,740 --> 00:12:00,340
We aren’t made of wood.

198
00:12:02,130 --> 00:12:03,370
How could we

199
00:12:03,370 --> 00:12:04,850
be completely emotionless?

200
00:12:04,850 --> 00:12:05,690
That’s right.

201
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:07,440
Without friends

202
00:12:07,550 --> 00:12:08,780
and the loved ones,

203
00:12:09,050 --> 00:12:10,590
