204
00:12:10,590 --> 00:12:11,790
I agree.

205
00:12:12,700 --> 00:12:13,950
Fun?

206
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:17,080
You carry the imperial bloodline.

207
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:18,840
