326
00:16:31,370 --> 00:16:32,350
Xiaoliu,

327
00:16:32,790 --> 00:16:34,270
you cannot die.

328
00:16:59,640 --> 00:17:01,160
With the look I have,

329
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:03,160
