Are you blind or what?

438
00:22:51,930 --> 00:22:53,040
I... I’m sorry.

439
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:09,680
The blood incense

440
00:23:10,020 --> 00:23:11,580
can make people hallucinate.

441
00:23:12,250 --> 00:23:13,530
Luckily, I have inner force.

442
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:02,730
Bad news, Your Highness.

443
00:24:02,730 --> 00:24:03,730
Something’s up.

444
00:24:03,730 --> 00:24:04,830
What happened?

445
00:24:05,210 --> 00:24:06,990
Yesterday, during His Majesty’s outing,

446
00:24:06,990 --> 00:24:08,580
he passed by the city moat,

447
00:24:08,580 --> 00:24:09,810
and saw someone fish a big stone

448
00:24:09,810 --> 00:24:11,240
out of the river.

449
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:13,890
It was carved with treacherous remarks.

450
00:24:15,010 --> 00:24:16,640
What do they say?

451
00:24:17,170 --> 00:24:20,110
Wei is dying. Yan will rule the world.

452
00:24:22,160 --> 00:24:24,240
Your Highness, are your feet alright?

453
00:24:28,270 --> 00:24:29,460
Then what?

454
00:24:31,810 --> 00:24:32,850
What happened?

455
00:24:33,520 --> 00:24:34,800
What did father say?

456
00:24:35,840 --> 00:24:38,500
His Majesty summoned Wei Guang, Zhao Gui,

457
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:39,250
and…

458
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:41,270
And Yuwen Huai.

459
00:24:41,270 --> 00:24:42,190
But I couldn’t find out

460
00:24:42,190 --> 00:24:43,540
