461
00:24:43,540 --> 00:24:45,570
But His Majesty

462
00:24:45,570 --> 00:24:47,840
killed General Song Zifu in the main hall.

463
00:24:56,940 --> 00:25:00,040
Song Zifu came from Yanbei,

464
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:01,470
and he was a general there.

465
00:25:02,090 --> 00:25:03,770
The north is Wei’s domain.

466
00:25:04,320 --> 00:25:05,600
They want Marquis Dingbei to die

467
00:25:05,600 --> 00:25:06,530
the most.

468
