and his army

470
00:25:10,870 --> 00:25:11,800
escorted Ms. Bai Sheng

471
00:25:12,270 --> 00:25:13,780
back to Yanbei.

472
00:25:14,980 --> 00:25:16,070
Father...

473
00:25:22,570 --> 00:25:24,300
Father is going to kill them.

474
00:25:25,280 --> 00:25:27,550
Your Highness, what should we do?

475
00:25:29,540 --> 00:25:31,100
Yan Xun is in danger.

476
00:25:32,070 --> 00:25:33,310
No wonder mother…

477
00:25:33,310 --> 00:25:34,190
Mother said those things

478
00:25:34,190 --> 00:25:35,130
to me and brother.

479
00:25:35,130 --> 00:25:35,840
She must know

480
00:25:35,840 --> 00:25:37,000
there is nothing we can do.

481
00:25:37,150 --> 00:25:37,920
I...

482
00:25:38,560 --> 00:25:40,120
I must tell Yan Xun.

483
00:25:40,120 --> 00:25:41,140
Your Highness.

484
00:25:41,140 --> 00:25:42,570
I have to save him.

485
00:25:42,570 --> 00:25:43,560
He must leave.

486
00:25:43,560 --> 00:25:44,530
And I’ll go with him.

487
00:25:44,530 --> 00:25:45,170
Your Highness.

488
00:25:45,570 --> 00:25:46,770
That’s his only chance of survival.

489
00:25:46,770 --> 00:25:47,120
Your Highness.

490
00:25:47,120 --> 00:25:48,370
- Please calm down.
- Back off!

491
00:25:48,370 --> 00:25:50,050
Yan Xun’s life is on the line!

492
00:25:50,380 --> 00:25:51,730
Don’t be a hindrance

493
00:25:51,730 --> 00:25:53,330
