I have mustered 30 elites of Yanbei

507
00:28:25,530 --> 00:28:27,400
to escort you to leave Chang’an overnight.

508
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:30,690
Thanks for the effort.

509
00:28:33,860 --> 00:28:35,010
I’ll stop

510
00:28:35,280 --> 00:28:36,970
at the west gate before ten

511
00:28:36,970 --> 00:28:38,090
