515
00:28:45,890 --> 00:28:46,850
Your Excellency.

516
00:28:46,850 --> 00:28:47,860
Say no more.

517
00:28:48,270 --> 00:28:49,500
I will take them back to Yanbei

518
00:28:49,500 --> 00:28:50,810
