519
00:29:04,510 --> 00:29:05,250
Stop!

520
00:29:05,570 --> 00:29:06,250
Who is it?

521
00:29:11,900 --> 00:29:12,710
I’m sorry

522
00:29:12,710 --> 00:29:14,320
