533
00:29:33,360 --> 00:29:35,390
Opening the gate at night without permission

534
00:29:35,840 --> 00:29:37,000
will get me killed.

535
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:39,440
If you don’t do it,

536
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:40,630
I’ll kill you now.

537
00:29:51,090 --> 00:29:51,860
Stop!

538
00:30:03,140 --> 00:30:04,390
Noble Consort.

539
00:30:06,430 --> 00:30:07,380
Mother.

540
00:30:09,640 --> 00:30:10,680
Where are you going?

541
00:30:12,930 --> 00:30:15,580
I’m bored in the palace,

542
00:30:15,790 --> 00:30:17,260
so I’d like to go out for a walk.

543
00:30:17,260 --> 00:30:18,190
Nonsense.

544
00:30:26,110 --> 00:30:26,580
Mother,

545
00:30:26,580 --> 00:30:27,980
you knew it, right?

546
00:30:28,300 --> 00:30:29,450
You knew that Yan Xun

547
00:30:29,450 --> 00:30:30,320
would be in trouble.

548
00:30:30,430 --> 00:30:31,630
So you said those things

549
00:30:31,630 --> 00:30:32,670
to me and my brother.

550
00:30:33,280 --> 00:30:34,160
Is that right?

551
00:30:34,470 --> 00:30:35,090
Yes.

552
00:30:35,300 --> 00:30:37,200
