557
00:30:44,470 --> 00:30:45,740
Then I’ll tell him to escape.

558
00:30:46,020 --> 00:30:47,380
I’ll leave with him.

559
00:30:48,990 --> 00:30:50,630
Your father has sent

560
00:30:50,630 --> 00:30:51,730
the troops to Yanbei

561
00:30:51,970 --> 00:30:53,710
to eliminate Marquis Dingbei and his family.

562
00:30:53,850 --> 00:30:56,210
Aren’t you afraid of death?

563
00:30:57,430 --> 00:30:58,580
Death is inevitable.

564
00:30:59,280 --> 00:31:00,470
I’d rather

565
00:31:00,810 --> 00:31:02,040
die with

566
00:31:02,040 --> 00:31:03,090
Yan Xun!

567
00:31:03,710 --> 00:31:04,560
Princess!

568
00:31:11,600 --> 00:31:13,000
