584
00:31:49,060 --> 00:31:50,840
Why?

585
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:52,570
Why should it end up like this?

586
00:31:52,570 --> 00:31:54,730
I don’t want this to happen!

587
00:31:58,410 --> 00:32:00,770
Mother, I’m begging you.

588
00:32:00,890 --> 00:32:02,460
Please let me out.

